metadata.name: Family Ties - LTB1
metadata.description:
Man with his grandson in a Khmu hilltribe village near Vang Vieng, Laos. Khmu people use their traditional scarves for multiple purposes, and one of them is for creating a sling to carry small children. Grandparents are usually left to look after the children whilst the parents are out working in the fields. 

Digital JPEG
Vang Vieng, Laos, July 2022
1 of 8
